{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ab422f46ab","title":"周恩来接见广西两派时谈北京政法学院《政法公社》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5a53f89693","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":23,"articleId":"ab422f46ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d99c770eb","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见广西两派时谈北京政法学院《政法公社》","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"},{"id":"25069f1d7e","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十三日零时15分至2时30分，周总理在人民大会堂接见了广西两派代表团部分代表。当谈到《政法公社》时，周总理指出：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"},{"id":"29a7aa0979","type":"paragraph","text":"“政法学院有个陈荣金，起初大家都支持他。你知道他到处煽动，反对中央，反对中央文革小组，太猖狂了。”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"},{"id":"bf2b287f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"《联指》代表插话：“这家伙到处去夺权，他们还到广西同另一个组织结合夺公安厅的权。”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"},{"id":"fdcd3d4fc8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志说：“政法公社就是到处去夺权。”","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"},{"id":"4b06491692","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理接着说：“我们现在已把他（指反革命分子陈荣金──编者）拘留了，”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab"}],"page":{"id":"a2ad2b05c3","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ab422f46ab","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}